<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The court of appeals may hold a prehearing conference or direct a judge of the court to hold a prehearing conference.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id52ddedc0-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/89/554/s4/e">Pub. L. 89–554, § 4(e)</ref>, <date date="1966-09-06">Sept. 6, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/622">80 Stat. 622</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
